%^BOLD%^WHITE%^ULINE%^Celestial Bloodline%^RESET%^

Your bloodline is blessed by a celestial power, either from a celestial ancestor or through divine intervention. Although this power drives you along the path of good, your fate (and alignment) is your own to determine.

%^WHITE%^BOLD%^Bloodline Arcana:%^RESET%^
You are protected from evil by your celestial blood, granting you 11 + sorcerer level / 2 spell damage resistance against casters with evil alignment.

%^WHITE%^BOLD%^Ascension:%^RESET%^
Your celestial blood is that of great and powerful creatures of divinity, granting you scaling resistance percent to acid of 20 + sorcerer level * 2.

%^WHITE%^BOLD%^Bonus Bloodline Skill%^RESET%^: healing

%^WHITE%^BOLD%^Bonus Spells%^RESET%^: bless, resist energy, dispel evil, break curse, angelic aspect, greater dispel magic, sunburst, gate
